<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="mountain-n">mountain <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'maʊntən/    美 /'maʊntn/  </p>
<p>[C]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>高山；山岳：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>climb a mountain 
爬山</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>mountain roads</strong> / <strong>villages</strong>
山路/山村</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I’m going to go camping <strong>in the mountains</strong>.
我要去山里露营。</p><footer>2013 北京</footer></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="a-mountain-of-mountains-of">a mountain of / mountains of</h3>
<p>1.<strong>大量；大堆：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a mountain of / mountains of work / debt / sandwiches 
一大堆的工作/债务/三明治</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The books are more precious to her than mountains of gold.
这些书对她来说比金山还珍贵。</p><footer>2017 浙江改</footer></div></div>